{"type": "article", "id": 39350, "title": "你有想过在洗澡时抿一口啤酒吗？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-03-30T23:48:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 2200, "name": "Moschino"}, {"id": 22765, "name": "Snask"}, {"id": 12862, "name": "Moment"}, {"id": 39082, "name": "Sèvres"}, {"id": 39083, "name": "Gufram"}, {"id": 39084, "name": "Arinze Stanley"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 219, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170330212957P2K1w8vVOijyh0bk.jpeg", "contents": "<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Shower Beer by Snask</h3><p>瑞典创意机构 <a href=\"http://www.snask.com/\">Snask</a> 显然深谙洗澡时喝上一小口啤酒带来的爽快感。继<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Make-Enemies-Gain-Fans-Entrepreneur/dp/3944334574/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1453814879&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=make+enemies+%26+gain+fans\">出书</a>和<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/vagmusik\">组乐队</a>之后，这群设计师决定打造一款不寻常的啤酒，为此他们和当地的小型酒厂 PangPang 一起设计了这款称为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/46393235/Shower-Beer\">Shower Beer</a> 艾尔啤酒。采用小瓶装规格的它刚好可以一手掌握，两三口就能喝完，很符合作为夜生活预热的定位。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170330213032zJMcFHxKwUpLm26R.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.773000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170330213031N4c7nfSDr6WIPuo3.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.679000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170330213029QXIB9TgYvs1Zywkc.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.040000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170330213032vToh0nQC3VUBxXgc.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.696000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>Sakura vase by nendo</h3><p>除了我们之前介绍的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/39078.html\">水母花瓶</a>之外，日本设计工作室 nendo 还会在米兰设计周上展出一款由法国陶瓷公司 <a href=\"http://sevresciteceramique.fr/\">Sèvres</a> 制作的樱花花瓶。花瓶内部“藏”有一段穿过圆洞的樱花树树枝，表面的凸起则巧妙地留住了花瓣随风飘落的瞬间，充满了春天的气息。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170330213217IfjA3YLNwMUDJkuc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.281333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201703302132187WfntFOmoL1hjIc8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170330213142uBKUsthCpkEOARge.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.165333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>Moschino Kisses Gufram by Jeremy Scott</h3><p>在即将开幕的米兰设计周上，由著名设计师 Jeremy Scott 主导的 Moschino 将会展出与意大利家具公司 <a href=\"http://www.gufram.it/it/\">Gufram</a> 联手打造的 Moschino Kisses Gufram 家具系列。这四件家具的造型分别参考了品牌最具辨识度的单品，比如变成衣柜的 Biker jacket 手拿包和做成沙发也不会让人感觉突兀的 Bocca 红唇手袋。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703302133114uUdgqm8p1oDawKR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170330213312G13lxTS6ViCm2Lz8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170330213312lBrjV5ysEKCd6uTX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170330213313X9RUtVuY2LE56S8y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Moment 2.0 by Moment</h3><p>来自美国西雅图的 <a href=\"https://momentlens.co/\">Moment</a> 是一个致力于优化手机拍摄效果的配件公司，旗下同名的外置镜头和手机壳都曾获得过不少媒体的好评。最近它又推出了名为 Moment 2.0 的迭代款，新增了适用于 Google Pixel 系列的款式以及为长时间摄影打造的可充电手机壳。除此之外，新版手机壳还采用了灵敏度更高的雷电接口快门，速度要比由蓝牙驱动的第一代快 75%。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/moment/moment-make-your-iphone-7-a-better-camera\">众筹链接</a>，售价从 25 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170330213329qepXz1cuksnrQLZl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170330213328vFtj7XeLWUaM51Nw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170330213328dTEk8OsVAayte2xW.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.558333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170330213329dG6mhLTA29MXbZxU.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.556250\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170330213329EgMKPtfz5rF0Nvm6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>MOKURU</h3><p>在日本设计师野出正和看来，比安全和易玩性更重要的是一款玩具能否给人带来足够的乐趣。最近，他根据友人在 20 年前提出的设计概念，开发了这款名为 MOKURU 的木制玩具。只要轻轻一推，它就会在桌面上翻滚，让人在灵活手指的同时舒缓焦虑。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1038095377/mokuru-the-amazing-desk-toy-that-you-can-take-anyw\">众筹链接</a>，售价从 14 加元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170330213435a3KnJqhyR2dmtvAW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561765\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170330213437csKtWET1puqOUQ3M.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560417\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201703302134465k4TqCEnJ8iN2Yht.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.559375\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170330213440Vd0yJziDGPQc5YLa.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.559375\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170330213447JpAwj67DhRgGH83W.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.963235\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170330213437hx4lZn0jqGuKzbsD.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.113235\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Pencil art by Arinze Stanley</h3><p>若不是看到尼日利亚艺术家 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/harinzeyart/\">Arinze Stanley</a> 绘画时的照片，你或许还会以为他是一个专门拍摄黑白肖像的摄影师。自学成才的 Stanley 会在下笔前花费大量时间钻研照片中人物的面部表情，再用铅笔耐心地还原出每一个细节，完成一幅作品最长需要花费 200 个小时的时间。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170330213813i82kV1YFglQtIE5s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.309333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170330213812czybLOxWduqi4CIo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.704000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170330213813aqYKrbgjmTXZvstA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.213333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170330213813lYKRf8WZeVDFys1O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.217333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}